  <bioghist id="aspace_5a466d7a1e75641cb71d3cf6af688b3e">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Inga Lohne Brauner was a reconstruction aide and nurse during World War I. She was the second wife of Olaf Brauner, a Cornell University professor and artist.</p>  </bioghist>
